[Poke:infinite-lives:Infinite Lives]
POKE #R$72BF(#N$72BF),#N$00

This removes the command;

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="address-1">#R$72BF(#N$72BF)</td>
      <td class="instruction">DEC (#REGhl)</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

Which is used to decrease the player life counter held at #R$66F0(#N$66F0).

